  "title": "Four people reported a close encounter with a stationary UFO in Peruíbe-SP [1995]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/29/four-people-reported-a-close-encounter-with-a-stationary-ufo-in-peruibe-sp/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1f6",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>OCT 14th, 1995</strong>. Time: 19h00. Duration: 30 minutes. On the beach in Peruíbe, on the south coast of the State of São Paulo, four people observed an unidentified flying object &#8220;coming out of the sea&#8221; about 100 meters away. According to the witnesses, the UFO was oval, white, appeared to be four centimeters at first and then increased in size &#8220;gradually&#8221;. The unknown object remained stationary during the sighting at about 100 meters high. The sighting was made with the naked eye, with cloudy sky. No photographs of the sighting were taken.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.404. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre a ocorrência de objeto voador na região de Peruíbe, Estado de São Paulo”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n",
  "excerpt": "<p>OCT 14th, 1995. Time: 19h00. Duration: 30 minutes. On the beach in Peruíbe, on the south coast of the State of São Paulo, four people observed an unidentified flying object &#8220;coming out of the sea&#8221; about 100 meters away. According to the witnesses, the UFO was oval, white, appeared to be four centimeters at first [&hellip;]</p>\n",
